(16490, 2889, 'overview', 'In a remote mountain village of 15th-century Joseon, humble headman Heung-do hears a rumor that any village hosting an exiled nobleman will be blessed with abundance and fortune. Hoping to bring prosperity to his impoverished community, he eagerly submits a petition to host one—unaware that his guest is none other than the fallen monarch, deposed boy-king Danjong.'),
(16491, 2889, 'release_date', '2026-02-04'),
(16492, 2889, 'popularity', '21.1226'),
