(16819, 2954, 'bio', 'Marissa Sue Prado (better known simply as Sue Prado) (born May 18, 1981) was a Filipina character actress best known for her performances in Philippine New Wave films such as the 2013 film, Barber\'s Tales, among other roles on Philippine film, television, and theater. She earned a Gawad Urian Award for Best Supporting Actress for the 2009 neo-noir film, Manila Skies.'),
