(2421, 1, '2026-04-16 19:57:42', '2026-04-16 19:57:42', 'Nam-bok, a middle-aged South Korean farmer is conscripted and assigned a mission to deliver a classified military document that may decide the fate of the war. After losing it while under attack from the enemy, he then faces a teenage North Korean soldier named Yeong-gwang who happens to acquire the secret document on his way to the North.', 'The Long Way Home', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'the-long-way-home__trashed', '', '', '2026-04-17 16:23:29', '2026-04-17 16:23:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jobsity/movies/the-long-way-home/', 0, 'movie', '', 0),
