(2445, 1, '2026-04-16 19:58:13', '2026-04-16 19:58:13', 'Anxiously awaiting the return of his new wife, Adolph finds solace in the words of a stranger. But comfort soon turns to destruction as old wounds are opened, insecurities are laid bare and former debts are settled.', 'Võlausaldajad', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'volausaldajad__trashed', '', '', '2026-04-17 16:23:29', '2026-04-17 16:23:29', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jobsity/movies/volausaldajad/', 0, 'movie', '', 0),
