(2807, 1, '2026-04-17 16:25:32', '2026-04-17 16:25:32', 'A man trapped in an endless sterile subway passageway sets out to find Exit 8. The rules of his quest are simple: do not overlook anything out of the ordinary. If you discover an anomaly, turn back immediately. If you don’t, carry on. Then leave from Exit 8. But even a single oversight will send him back to the beginning. Will he ever reach his goal and escape this infinite corridor?', 'Exit 8', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'exit-8', '', '', '2026-04-17 16:25:32', '2026-04-17 16:25:32', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jobsity/movies/exit-8/', 0, 'movie', '', 0),
