(2990, 1, '2026-04-17 16:32:16', '2026-04-17 16:32:16', 'Assassin bride flirting with a handsome general! He Lian was instructed to marry General Murong, only to steal the thing that matters the most to him. But General Murong found out that the flirty girl who took his breath away was the person who rescued the assassin from his camp and caused him a great deal of embarrassment! What goes around comes around. This time, he finally gets a chance to turn the table. He Lian is good at pretending to be delicate and helpless. How will the general beat her in this round?', 'Fall in Love With My King', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'fall-in-love-with-my-king', '', '', '2026-04-17 16:32:16', '2026-04-17 16:32:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jobsity/movies/fall-in-love-with-my-king/', 0, 'movie', '', 0),
