(3074, 1, '2026-04-17 16:34:24', '2026-04-17 16:34:24', 'A stolen computer disk contains the location of a hidden tresaure trove. It\'s up to the sexy ladies of LETHAL (Legion to Ensure Total Harmony and Law) to find the treasure before the bad guys do.', 'L.E.T.H.A.L. Ladies: Return to Savage Beach', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'l-e-t-h-a-l-ladies-return-to-savage-beach', '', '', '2026-04-17 16:34:24', '2026-04-17 16:34:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/jobsity/movies/l-e-t-h-a-l-ladies-return-to-savage-beach/', 0, 'movie', '', 0),
